### [2 Kings (2 Samuel) Chapter 20](../../../bib/kjv/sa2020.htm#001.md)

[2 Kings (2 Samuel)](../../../bib/kjv/sa2001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">sa2 20:0</span></span>

Overview

[Sa2 20:1](../../../bib/kjv/sa2020.htm#001.md), By occasion of the quarrel,
Sheba makes a party in Israel; [Sa2
20:3](../../../bib/kjv/sa2020.htm#003.md), David's ten concubines are put
in confinement for life; [Sa2 20:4](../../../bib/kjv/sa2020.htm#004.md),
Amasa, made captain over Judah, is slain by Joab; [Sa2
20:14](../../../bib/kjv/sa2020.htm#014.md), Joab pursues Sheba unto Abel;
[Sa2 20:16](../../../bib/kjv/sa2020.htm#016.md), A wise woman saves the
city by Sheba's head; [Sa2 20:23](../../../bib/kjv/sa2020.htm#023.md),
David's officers.

